            <h5 class=\card-title\>Our Privacy Promise</h5>
            <p class=\card-text\>At WhiteCoat, we are committed to protecting your privacy and personal health information. Our platform is designed with privacy as a core principle, not an afterthought.</p>
            
            <h6 class=\mt-4\>Data Separation by Design</h6>
            <ul>
                <li>Patient identities and test results are permanently separated</li>
                <li>Phlebotomists only see collection information, not personal data</li>
                <li>Laboratories receive samples with system-generated codes only</li>
                <li>Results are delivered through secure, authenticated channels</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h6 class=\mt-4\>Information We Collect</h6>
            <p>We only collect information necessary to provide our services:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Contact information for scheduling and communication</li>
                <li>Payment information for processing orders</li>
                <li>Test preferences and collection details</li>
                <li>Anonymous health data for aggregate analysis (optional)</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h6 class=\mt-4\>HIPAA Compliance</h6>
            <p>WhiteCoat is designed to be HIPAA compliant. We implement administrative, physical, and technical safeguards to protect your health information.</p>
            
            <div class=\alert
alert-info
mt-4\>
                <i class=\fas
fa-shield-alt
me-2\></i>
                <strong>Privacy First:</strong> Your privacy is protected at every step of the process.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
